title: Incredible Hulk vs. Superman
description:
Its a one shot feature published by Marvel Comics in July 1999. It features Hulk vs Superman and also Lex Luthor as the main villain. Luthor creates a Hulk robot and makes Superman fight real Hulk and has also some other plans. 

The scans are vary good. I decided to post it as it would be a good addition to Citaltras&#039; Hulk project.

Enjoy and Seed
